Invocation Name: shape up
des:
Are you busy throughout the week? Are you constantly on the go? Do you not have time to spend hours at the gym but still want to stay fit? Shape Up is your solution. This skill provides a quick workout for every day of the week to keep you healthy and energized to continue your day. 
Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
